美国专利和商标局（USPTO）28日<a href="http://www.conceivablytech.com/8165/business/google-patents-deep-secret-of-the-internet">授予了</a>Google一项专利：“<a href="http://patft1.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO1&amp;Sect2=HITOFF&amp;d=PALL&amp;p=1&amp;u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsrchnum.htm&amp;r=1&amp;f=G&amp;l=50&amp;s1=7,971,137.PN.&amp;OS=PN/7,971,137&amp;RS=PN/7,971,137">检测和拒绝令人生厌的文件</a>”。<i>
